<template>
  <v-md-editor v-model="text" height="400px"></v-md-editor>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'MarkdownView',
    props: ['location'],
    methods: {
        getNoteInfo() {
            this.$axios.get('/Note/GetNoteInfo?fileLocation=' + this.location).then(response => {
                console.log(response.data);
            })
        }
    },
    mounted() {
        this.getNoteInfo()
    },
}
</script>
